sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Django as Django (views.py)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    %% ── Save a preset ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    User->>Browser: Fill prediction form, click "Save as Preset"
    Browser->>Browser: JS copies field values into modal hidden inputs
    Browser->>Browser: Open save-preset modal
    User->>Browser: Enter preset name, click Save
    Browser->>Django: POST /flows/presets/save/ (preset_name + field values)
    Django->>DB: INSERT InputPreset (user, name, input_values)
    Django-->>Browser: 200 + HX-Trigger: presets-updated + toast message

    %% ── Load a preset ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    User->>Browser: Select preset from dropdown
    Browser->>Django: GET /flows/presets/load/?preset_id=<id>
    Django->>DB: SELECT InputPreset WHERE id=<id> AND user=request.user
    Django-->>Browser: HTMX partial — prediction-inputs grid with pre-filled values
    Browser->>Browser: Swap #prediction-inputs with pre-filled fields

    %% ── Delete a preset ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    User->>Browser: Click Delete on a preset row (Settings page)
    Browser->>Django: POST /flows/presets/<id>/delete/
    Django->>DB: DELETE InputPreset WHERE id=<id> AND user=request.user
    Django-->>Browser: HTMX partial — updated presets list
